# =============================================================================
# REAPER Sound Definitions
# =============================================================================
# 
# This file defines metadata for custom audio assets that cannot be derived
# from the waveform alone. Each sound gets:
#
#  - loop_start: Sample offset where loop begins (0 = no loop)
#  - loop_end: Sample offset where loop ends (0 = end of file)
#  - pitch_variance: Random pitch shift in cents (+/- value, 0 = none)
#  - reverb_depth: Override reverb amount (0-127, or 255 for map default)
#  - priority: Voice stealing priority (0-255, higher = more important)
#
# Sample rates: 44100 samples = 1 second
#
# =============================================================================

